Hi,
Thank You for checking out my work.

I suspect you have node installed..:)

To spin up the calculator please:
- clone this repo
- cd FullStackCalculator/backend
- npm install
- node server
- in browser open localhost:8888

The app has all the required functions and can be used with 
keyboard as well.
(keyCodes set up for Macbook Air, US keyboard)

0...9     => numbers
.         => dot
a         => addition
s         => subtraction
x         => multiplication
d         => division
enter     => equal
m         => add to memory
r         => retrieve from memory
backspace => clear

